longBusinessSummary: Golden Sun Mining Corp. does not have significant operations. Previously, it was engaged in the exploration and evaluation of mineral properties. The company intends to acquire strategic mining assets and undertake precious and base-metals mineral exploration activities. The company was formerly known as Silver Sun Resource Corp. and changed its name to Golden Sun Mining Corp. in January 2013. Golden Sun Mining Corp. was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
